    "There were 10 FAQs regarding the ability to perform specific activities such as walking, running and driving after TKR (Table 6).",
    "Of the responses, 10/10 (100%) were deemed to be accurate (mean grade 4.8), and 10/10 (100%) were deemed to be relevant (mean grade 5.0).",
    "There were 7 FAQs regarding alternatives to TKR and variants of TKR such as bilateral TKR, robotic TKR and partial knee replacement (Table 7).",
